					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-715443#post-1885479</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-715443/scp-1534#post-1885479</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2013 08:09:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>thedeadlymoose</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>732274</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>However, SCP-1534 shows a marked dislike of corpses and other non-skeletal tissues from cadavers, and will actively avoid them. It appears to favor human bones over all other types of bones, but will consume any type of bone given to it.</p> </blockquote> <p>This is confusing because you don't state that this is a vulture.</p> <p>My advice &#8212; just say &quot;SCP-1534-1 is a male lammergeier, or bearded vulture (Gypaetus barbatus), estimated to be ten years old. &quot; and leave the rest the same.</p> <p>Otherwise, this is really pretty neat. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
