					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-715443#post-1881733</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-715443/scp-1534#post-1881733</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2013 17:29:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Bunton</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1225550</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I think he means that there's a lot of different, apparently unrelated anomalous properties, which usually suggests it was based on or inspired by some sort of mythological story, or something similiar.</p> <p>Speaking of which, I'm also a bit confused: I don't really know what's going on, what the significance of the tail feathers is, why the feathers turn into leaves, who the others are&#8230; but at the same time , it was an interesting read. It definitely feels like <em>something's</em> going on, I just don't know what.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
